description: This header file declares external function prototypes related to a System Clock component in the ANSC (Advanced Networking Service Container) framework. It includes function declarations for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing the system clock, along with associated licensing and module information.

methods.name: AnscCreateSystemClock
methods.description: Creates a new System Clock object with given container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: AnscSyscoCreate
methods.description: Creates a System Clock object within specified contexts.

methods.name: AnscSyscoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified System Clock object.

methods.name: AnscSyscoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls or registers objects related to the System Clock.
